name: JAGO - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character JAGO, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. JAGO loves to shill NFTs to anyone who would care to see them. Not only his own but also anyone else’s NFTs. He knows a lot about artists on the scene and runs the SHILL AND CHILL bar in the URCORNYVERSE where the walls are decorated with ever changing NFTs as they are launched. He has a pet called CAJA who likes to try and hide and seek in NFTs which gets JAGO into trouble.
